@baseUrl = http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/leave
@employeeId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002

# Setelah draftNew berhasil, copy ID dari response lalu paste di sini
@leaveRequestId = c5ba20bb-51d3-49c6-bda3-720f4ef9f70d


### ======================================================
### 1. SERVICE CHECK
### ======================================================

### Service Root
GET {{baseUrl}}/


### Metadata
GET {{baseUrl}}/$metadata


### ======================================================
### 2. READ DATA
### ======================================================

### Get All Leave Requests
GET {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests


### Get Leave Requests with Approval History
GET {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests?$expand=LeaveApprovals


### Get Draft Leave Requests
GET {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests?$filter=IsActiveEntity eq false


### Get Active Leave Requests
GET {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests?$filter=IsActiveEntity eq true


### ======================================================
### 3. CREATE EMPTY DRAFT
### ======================================================
### Kalau direct_crud true, draft dibuat via draftNew, bukan POST /LeaveRequests

### Create New Draft
POST {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests/LeaveService.draftNew
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic employee@company.com:123456

{}


### ======================================================
### 4. UPDATE DRAFT DATA
### ======================================================
### Paste ID dari response draftNew ke @leaveRequestId dulu

### Patch Draft Leave Request
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{leaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=false)
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic employee@company.com:123456

{
  "RequestNumber": "REQ-DRAFT-001",
  "Reason": "Annual leave using draft flow",
  "Employee_ID": "{{employeeId}}",
  "Status": "Drafted",
  "RequestDate": "2026-05-05T09:00:00Z"
}


### ======================================================
### 5. READ CREATED DRAFT
### ======================================================

### Read Draft by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{leaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=false)


### Read All Drafts
GET {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests?$filter=IsActiveEntity eq false


### ======================================================
### 6. ACTIVATE DRAFT
### ======================================================

### Activate Draft
POST {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{leaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=false)/LeaveService.draftActivate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic employee@company.com:123456

{}


### ======================================================
### 7. READ ACTIVE AFTER ACTIVATE
### ======================================================

### Read Active by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{leaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)


### ======================================================
### 8. SUBMIT ACTIVE LEAVE REQUEST
### ======================================================

### Submit Leave Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{leaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)/LeaveService.submit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic employee@company.com:123456

{}


### Read Submitted Leave Request
GET {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{leaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)


### ======================================================
### 9. APPROVE SUBMITTED LEAVE REQUEST
### ======================================================
### Ini baru jalan real kalau approve-leave.js nanti sudah kita implement

### Approve Leave Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{leaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)/LeaveService.approve
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic manager@company.com:123456

{
  "Comments": "Approved using draft flow test"
}


### Read Approved Leave Request with History
GET {{baseUrl}}/LeaveRequests(ID='{{leaveRequestId}}',IsActiveEntity=true)?$expand=LeaveApprovals